// diagramType: sequence-diagram
// Eraser /render/elements (scale 3, theme light, colorMode pastel). The embedded .svg wraps
// this PNG render (the Eraser API/MCP export PNG only); regenerate by re-feeding this DSL.
title Runtime view: semantic search (read-only)
colorMode pastel
typeface clean

Consumer [icon: user, color: blue]
API [icon: server, color: green, label: "TarifCore API (FastAPI main.py)"]
Embedder [icon: cpu, color: green, label: "Embedder (get_embedder)"]
Repo [icon: database, color: green, label: "ServingRepository"]
DB [icon: database, color: green, label: "PostgreSQL + pgvector"]

Consumer > API: GET /api/v1/search with q and limit
activate API
API > Repo: Depends(get_repository), per-request connection
API > Embedder: embed(q)
Embedder > API: vector, 1024-dim e5 or 16-dim offline stub
alt [label: "vector dim mismatches schema vector 1024"] {
  API > Consumer: HTTP 501, search honestly unavailable, no fake results
}
else [label: "dimensions match"] {
  API > Repo: search_by_embedding(vector, limit)
  Repo > DB: parameterised pgvector cosine query, ORDER BY embedding distance, LIMIT n
  DB > Repo: rows, frozen records
  Repo > API: _row_to_record to list of TariffRecord
  API > Consumer: 200 JSON, list of SearchHit with rank and record
}
deactivate API
API > API: read-only path, no LLM client importable here, enforced by test_serving_boundary.py AST check
